headline: Marriott International Announces Release Date For First Quarter 2025 Earnings
summary: Marriott International, Inc. (Nasdaq: MAR) will report first quarter 2025 earnings results on Tuesday, May 6, 2025, at approximately 7:00 a.m. Eastern Time (ET). The company will hold a conference call for the investment community on Tuesday, May 6, 2025, at 8:30 a.m. (ET). Marriott International's President and Chief Executive Officer, Anthony Capuano, and Chief Financial Officer and Executive Vice President, Development, Leeny Oberg, will discuss the company's performance.
